<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>思渊1 · 哲学深潜</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
      background: #f8fafc;
      color: #1e293b;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    a {
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    nav {
      background: white;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 10;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 1280px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }
    .nav-inner {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      height: 64px;
    }
    .logo {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    .logo span {
      color: #4f46e5;
    }
    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 24px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .nav-links a {
      color: #64748b;
    }
    .nav-links a.active {
      color: #4f46e5;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, #f8fafc 0%, #eef2ff 100%);
      padding: 80px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 36px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .hero h1 span {
      color: #4f46e5;
    }
    .hero p {
      color: #64748b;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto 32px;
    }
    .buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .btn {
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 500;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .btn.primary {
      background: #4f46e5;
      color: white;
    }
    .btn.secondary {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
      color: #334155;
    }
    .section {
      padding: 60px 0;
    }
    .section-white {
      background: white;
    }
    .section-gray {
      background: #f8fafc;
    }
    .section-title {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
    .section-title h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .section-title p {
      color: #64748b;
    }
    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
    }
    .card {
      background: #f8fafc;
      padding: 24px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }
    .card h3 {
      margin: 16px 0 8px;
    }
    .card p {
      color: #64748b;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .flex-row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 32px;
    }
    .flex-1 {
      flex: 1;
    }
    .book-item {
      background: white;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .book-num {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      background: #eef2ff;
      color: #4f46e5;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .timeline {
      border-left: 2px solid #ddd;
      padding-left: 20px;
      margin-left: 8px;
    }
    .timeline-item {
      position: relative;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .timeline-item::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: -28px;
      top: 4px;
      width: 12px;
      height: 12px;
      background: #4f46e5;
      border-radius: 50%;
    }
    .timeline-date {
      color: #4f46e5;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .tools {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 12px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .tool {
      padding: 16px;
      background: #f8fafc;
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }
    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      padding: 32px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      background: white;
      color: #64748b;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

<nav>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <div class="logo">思渊<span>·深潜</span></div>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a class="active">首页</a >
        <a>经典</a >
        <a>思维工具</a >
        <a>路径</a >
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>用<span>深度思考</span>对抗浅薄</h1>
    <p>从苏格拉底到维特根斯坦，从形而上学到心灵哲学 ——
这里没有速成鸡汤，只有严谨的论证与清晰的概念地图。</p >
    <div class="buttons">
      <button class="btn primary">查看学习路径</button>
      <button class="btn secondary">经典导读</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-title">
      <h2>哲学的核心领域</h2>
      <p>从三个基本问题出发，建立你的思考框架</p >
    </div>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>形而上学</h3>
        <p>存在是什么？实在的结构如何？自由意志是否可能？</p >
        <small>经典问题：忒修斯之船</small>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>认识论</h3>
        <p>我们如何知道？知识的边界在哪？信念如何被证成？</p >
        <small>思想实验：盖梯尔问题</small>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>伦理学</h3>
        <p>我们应该如何生活？对错的标准是什么？</p >
        <small>思想实验：电车难题</small>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-gray">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="flex-row">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <h2>必读经典</h2>
        <div class="book-item">
          <div class="book-num">1</div>
          <div>
            <strong>《理想国》· 柏拉图</strong>
            <p>洞穴喻、灵魂三分、哲人王 —— 西方哲学总注解。</p >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="book-item">
          <div class="book-num">2</div>
          <div>
            <strong>《第一哲学沉思集》· 笛卡尔</strong>
            <p>“我思故我在”与普遍怀疑的方法。</p >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="book-item">
          <div class="book-num">3</div>
          <div>
            <strong>《纯粹理性批判》· 康德</strong>
            <p>哥白尼式革命：人为自然立法。</p >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex-1">
        <h2>思想脉络</h2>
        <div class="timeline">
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-date">古代 · 前6世纪 – 5世纪</div>
            <div>苏格拉底 · 柏拉图 · 亚里士多德</div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-date">中世纪 · 5世纪 – 15世纪</div>
            <div>奥古斯丁 · 阿奎那 · 奥卡姆</div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-date">近代 · 17世纪 – 18世纪</div>
            <div>笛卡尔 · 斯宾诺莎 · 莱布尼茨 · 休谟 · 康德</div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="timeline-date">19世纪 – 20世纪</div>
            <div>黑格尔 · 尼采 · 维特根斯坦 · 海德格尔 · 萨特</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-title">
      <h2>论证与思维工具</h2>
      <p>哲学不仅是知识，更是一套思考的方法</p >
    </div>
    <div class="tools">
      <div class="tool">逻辑谬误手册</div>
      <div class="tool">思想实验库</div>
      <div class="tool">论证结构图</div>
      <div class="tool">概念辨析</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>© 2026 思渊 · 哲学深潜 — 保持怀疑，持续追问</p >
  <p>一个开源哲学学习项目</p >
</footer>

</body>
</html>
